description: Lists the historical executions for the export.

parameters.name: ExportArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for this export.

nested_items.name: ExecutionId
nested_items.description: The ID for this specific execution.

nested_items.name: ExecutionStatus
nested_items.description: The status of this specific execution.

nested_items.name: CompletedAt
nested_items.description: The time when the execution was completed.

nested_items.name: CreatedAt
nested_items.description: The time when the execution was created.

nested_items.name: LastUpdatedAt
nested_items.description: The time when the execution was last updated.

nested_items.name: StatusCode
nested_items.description: The code for the status of the execution.

nested_items.name: StatusReason
nested_items.description: The reason for the failed status.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token to retrieve the next set of results.
